<h1 class="hero-h">Claude for <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">fitness &amp; wellness.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Independent fitness and wellness owners wear every hat — coach, marketer, ops manager, customer service. AI does not replace the coaching, but it removes the parts of the business that pull you away from coaching. Here is the practical workflow.</p>
</div></div>

<section><div class="sec-inner"><span class="lbl">The 5 workflows</span><h2 class="h2">Where AI saves owner time</h2>
    <p class="body"><strong>1. Program documentation.</strong> Workout templates, nutrition guides, member-facing program descriptions.</p>
    <p class="body"><strong>2. Member communications.</strong> Welcome sequences, check-ins, birthday messages, reactivation outreach.</p>
    <p class="body"><strong>3. Social media.</strong> Daily Instagram, transformation stories (with permission), educational content.</p>
    <p class="body"><strong>4. Coach training and SOPs.</strong> Standardize the coaching experience across staff.</p>
    <p class="body"><strong>5. Retention sequences.</strong> Member behavior signals churn risk; targeted outreach addresses it.</p>
    </div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner"><span class="lbl">What stays human</span><h2 class="h2">The coaching core</h2>
    <p class="body">The actual coaching relationship. AI cannot replace presence with a member.</p>
    <p class="body">Form correction. Always human.</p>
    <p class="body">Recovery from injury. Personalized, human work.</p>
    <p class="body">Difficult member conversations (refunds, behavior issues, etc.). Personal touch matters.</p>
    </div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner"><span class="lbl">Realistic deployment</span><h2 class="h2">For a small gym or studio</h2>
    <p class="body">Owner uses Claude Pro ($20/mo) for personal workflow. Plus a one-time setup of Member Communications Project (~$500-$1,500 if outsourced).</p>
    <p class="body">Typical time savings: 5-8 hours/week of owner time, redirected to higher-value coaching and member experience.</p>
    </div></section>

